---
title: Sunny & Spiced Chicken Quinoa Bowls with Tomato Salad, Feta, Scallions & Greek Yogurt Sauce
description: Power yoga, power nap, power stance: all pretty important. But there’s only one we’d choose to power up with at the end of the day, and that’s this layered, textured, flavorful bowl. In it you’ll find tender Turkish-spiced chicken over light and fluffy garlic-scallion quinoa, tossed with a tomato-cucumber salad topped with feta, more scallions, and a drizzle of creamy Greek yogurt sauce. Power(bowl) to the people!
